    <article class="markdown-body entry-content container-lg" itemprop="text"><h1 dir="auto"><a id="user-content-how-to-add-a-new-fingerprint" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#how-to-add-a-new-fingerprint"><svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z"></path></svg></a>How to Add a New Fingerprint</h1>
<p dir="auto">This tutorial goes through the steps of adding a new fingerprint to the fingerprint database.
These steps are:</p>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>Identify the technology you'd like to fingerprint</li>
<li>Pick a category for it</li>
<li>Find Web sites that use the technology</li>
<li>Examine the Web sites and scope out the fingerprint</li>
<li>Write code to capture the fingerprint</li>
<li>Repeat</li>
<li>Test</li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto">Next, we'll look at the steps in more detail.</p>
<h2 dir="auto"><a id="user-content-identify-the-technology" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#identify-the-technology"><svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z"></path></svg></a>Identify the Technology</h2>
<p dir="auto">This step requires expert knowledge.
You should research popular Web technologies currently in use and keep up to date with the trends.
Places to start include sites like <a href="https://trends.builtwith.com/" rel="nofollow">builtwith.com</a>.</p>
<p dir="auto">For the purposes of this tutorial, we will focus on <a href="https://www.hotjar.com/" rel="nofollow">hotjar.com</a>.</p>
